name: Informants of Prophesied Storms
description: Hailing, shockingly, from within the storms that rumble over the plains of Kharth, the Informants of Prophesied Storms mentioned in goatlichâ€™s prophecy foretelling the end of days. Now, blessed with a sundew lotus due to their ties with the Groodu, they look towards the future with a glint in their eye. Their future is bright. The only question: what comes next?
